      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"Self-care\"... that's a strange way to put it. But I get what you mean about the noise. It's just so loud all the time. I look at the ground down there and it doesn't look scary, it just looks... silent. Like a place where I don't have to try anymore. Do you think it's wrong to want to just check out of the tour? To say I've seen enough and just step off the path?",
